{"words":[{"word":"myron","count":4},{"word":"sing","count":4},{"word":"others","count":3},{"word":"hymn","count":3},{"word":"sentinel","count":3},{"word":"ceremony","count":2},{"word":"choir","count":2},{"word":"performance","count":2},{"word":"never","count":2},{"word":"praises","count":2},{"word":"song","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"everyone","count":2},{"word":"laureate","count":1},{"word":"and-and","count":1},{"word":"hide","count":1},{"word":"seek","count":1},{"word":"waiting","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"caused","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"rehearse","count":1},{"word":"i-i'm","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"listen","count":1},{"word":"music","count":1},{"word":"recite","count":1},{"word":"lyrics","count":1},{"word":"rehearsals","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"practicing","count":1},{"word":"composed","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"teacher","count":1},{"word":"calls","count":1},{"word":"heretic","count":1},{"word":"poets","count":1},{"word":"complain","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"eager","count":1},{"word":"stage","count":1},{"word":"dreams","count":1},{"word":"dashed","count":1},{"word":"patero","count":1},{"word":"shia's","count":1},{"word":"voices","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"harmony","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"young","count":1},{"word":"realize","count":1},{"word":"heresy","count":1},{"word":"grave","count":1},{"word":"offense","count":1},{"word":"i-i","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"order","count":1},{"word":"wants","count":1},{"word":"songs","count":1},{"word":"written","count":1},{"word":"criminals","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"rhythm","count":1},{"word":"became","count":1},{"word":"end","count":1},{"word":"barely","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"forgotten","count":1},{"word":"supposed","count":1},{"word":"sound","count":1},{"word":"books","count":1},{"word":"state","count":1},{"word":"praise","count":1},{"word":"leads","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"abundant","count":1},{"word":"lands","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"um","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"huh","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"figured","count":1},{"word":"sincerity","count":1},{"word":"truly","count":1},{"word":"matters","count":1},{"word":"pray","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"You... You're the Laureate! And-and you are...?","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Hide and seek... right. Myron and the others are waiting for me. Sorry, I’ve caused you trouble...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"What? Of course not. The ceremony is coming up and the choir still has so much to rehearse. I-I'm fine...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"It's just... before the performance, the choir has to listen to the same music, recite the same lyrics, and do the same rehearsals every day.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"What's more, the hymn we're practicing... it was composed by bad people. Teacher calls them \"heretic poets.\"","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Myron and the others never complain. They're always eager to sing praises to the Sentinel on stage.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"But now, their dreams are all dashed because of me. Myron, Patero, and Shia's voices are in perfect harmony. But I can never keep up.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"And I don't like this hymn. Myron and the others are too young to realize that heresy is a grave offense... But I know...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"I-I just don't understand why the Order wants us to sing songs written by criminals.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"The more I thought about it, the more out of rhythm I became. In the end, I could barely sing at all.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"That song just now? I... I've already forgotten how it's supposed to sound.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"A hymn... as the books state, is a song of praise for the Sentinel who leads the lost to the abundant lands...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Oh... um... I didn't want to hold everyone back, and I really wanted to help everyone have a great performance at the ceremony.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Huh? No...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Thanks to you, I've figured it out.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Sincerity is what truly matters when we pray and sing praises to the Sentinel.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003}]}